If you forget your password, you can use the Forgotten Password option:
Click on ‘More Options’ to expand the dialogue box and select the 
       ‘Forgotten your Password’ link.
Enter your valid ONS email address and click on the ‘I’m not a robot’ check box.
Once you select the ‘EMAIL MY PASSWORD’ button, an email will be sent to your inbox containing a link which will allow you to change the password.
